FBIS4-58597 "drnes087_j_94007" FBIS-NES-94-087 Daily Report 5 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Update on Events 4, 5 May; Fighting Reported in Dhamar Update on Events 4, 5 May; Fighting Reported in Dhamar Usage, Transport of Weapons Banned JN0505061994 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 0607 GMT 5 May 94 JN0505061994 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Unscheduled announcement] [Text] An important announcement to all brother citizens: The Interior Ministry would like to inform the brother citizens that carrying weapons around in the capital is strictly prohibited. The ministry will take all measures against violators. Firing is also strictly forbidden. Violators will be legally prosecuted. May God grant us success.
